data.description: Welcome to this lovely townhome in the gated community of Verano.  Centrally located to shopping, dining, hospitals, and Durbin Pavilion. BRAND NEW ROOF 2022, Smart lighting and garage door opener.  Pre-wired for home theatre speakers.  Nest smart thermostats both upstairs and downstairs.  Nest Hello Video doorbell.  Kitchen has a spacious breakfast bar.  Enjoy the peaceful serene privacy on your screened in lanai. Both bedrooms have walk in closets and both bathrooms have garden tubs. Enjoy maintenance free living with fitness center, club pool and pavilion.
